stateDiagram-v2
    %% ===== ATTEMPT LIFECYCLE =====
    [*] --> NotStarted: Create Attempt Record
    
    NotStarted --> Started: Student Clicks "Start Quiz"
    Started --> Submitted: Student Submits Attempt
    
    Submitted --> CheckQuestionType: System Checks\nQuestion Types
    
    CheckQuestionType --> OnlyMCQ: Only MCQ\nQuestions
    CheckQuestionType --> HasWritten: Has Written\nQuestions
    
    OnlyMCQ --> AutoGraded: Auto-grade MCQs\nCalc Final Score
    AutoGraded --> Graded: Mark isGraded=true
    
    HasWritten --> PendingGrading: Mark as Pending\nManual Grading
    PendingGrading --> InstructorReview: Instructor Grades\nWritten Answers
    InstructorReview --> Graded: Mark isGraded=true
    
    Graded --> CalcXP: Calculate XP\nfor Student
    CalcXP --> CheckBadgeUnlock: Check Badge\nConditions
    CheckBadgeUnlock --> BadgeUnlocked: Unlock Badges\nif Thresholds Met
    BadgeUnlocked --> CheckPowerUpUnlock
    
    CheckBadgeUnlock --> CheckPowerUpUnlock: No Badges\nUnlocked
    CheckPowerUpUnlock --> PowerUpUnlocked: Unlock PowerUps\nif XP Thresholds Met
    PowerUpUnlocked --> Completed
    
    CheckPowerUpUnlock --> Completed: No PowerUps\nUnlocked
    Completed --> [*]
    
    %% ===== QUIZ LIFECYCLE =====
    [*] --> Draft: Instructor Creates\nQuiz
    
    Draft --> Editing: Edit Questions\n& Settings
    Editing --> Draft
    
    Draft --> Published: Instructor\nPublishes Quiz
    Published --> Active: Deadline Not\nPassed Yet
    
    Active --> QuizInProgress: Student Can\nStart Attempt
    QuizInProgress --> Active
    
    Active --> Expired: Deadline\nPassed
    Expired --> Closed: Quiz Closed\nNo More Attempts

    
    %% ===== GAMIFICATION UNLOCKS (After Grading) =====
    Completed --> GamificationCheck: Check XP
    GamificationCheck --> XPCalculated: XP Updated
    XPCalculated --> PowerUpCheck: Check PowerUp Thresholds
    PowerUpCheck --> PowerUpUnlocked: PowerUps Unlocked
    PowerUpUnlocked --> BadgeCheck: Check Badge Conditions
    BadgeCheck --> BadgesUnlocked: Badges Unlocked
    BadgesUnlocked --> [*]
